Good morning.

2847
02:12:57,970 --> 02:12:59,972
I've, uh, called this
meeting to discuss

2848
02:12:59,972 --> 02:13:02,474
a new type of check fraud
and counterfeiting

2849
02:13:02,474 --> 02:13:04,476
which the unsub is washing
and altering checks

2850
02:13:04,977 --> 02:13:06,478
then passing them
throughout Arizona.

2851
02:13:06,979 --> 02:13:10,983
(panting)

2852
02:13:10,983 --> 02:13:12,484
This unsub is a big dog

2853
02:13:12,484 --> 02:13:14,486
