02:13:17,990 --> 02:13:20,993
Sorry I'm late.

2856
02:13:20,993 --> 02:13:22,995
Sorry.

2857
02:13:26,498 --> 02:13:30,002
We have a recovered check
on Agent Reiter's desk.

2858
02:13:30,002 --> 02:13:32,004
Why don't we step out
to the bullpen?

2859
02:13:36,508 --> 02:13:40,512
There's impressions
on every line.

2860
02:13:40,512 --> 02:13:44,016
Looks like the original amount
was for $60.

2861
02:13:48,020 --> 02:13:49,021
Mind if I take a look?

2862
02:13:52,524 --> 02:13:55,527
Cashed in Flagstaff
a week ago.

2863
02:13:57,529 --> 02:14:00,532
Cost the bank $16,000.

2864
02:14:00,532 --> 02:14:02,534
It's a real check.

2865
02:14:02,534 --> 02:14:04,536
Yeah.

2866
02:14:04,536 --> 02:14:05,537
Yeah. It's been washed.

2867
02:14:05,537 --> 02:14:07,539
The only thing original
is the signature.

2868
02:14:07,539 --> 02:14:09,541
But it's perfect, Carl.
I mean...

2869
02:14:09,541 --> 02:14:12,044
I mean, this isn't
hydrochloride or bleach.

2870
02:14:12,044 --> 02:14:14,046
No.

2871
02:14:14,546 --> 02:14:16,048
Something new.

2872
02:14:16,048 --> 02:14:18,050
Maybe a nail polish remover
where the acetone

2873
02:14:18,050 --> 02:14:20,052
removes the ink that's
not been printed?

2874
02:14:24,056 --> 02:14:27,059
How did you do it, Frank?

2875
02:14:27,059 --> 02:14:30,062
How did you cheat on the
bar exam in Louisiana?

2876
02:14:35,567 --> 02:14:38,570
I didn't cheat.

2877
02:14:38,570 --> 02:14:42,574
I studied for two weeks
and I passed.

2878
02:14:43,575 --> 02:14:46,078
Is that the truth, Frank?

2879
02:14:46,078 --> 02:14:48,080
Is that the truth?

2880
02:14:48,080 --> 02:14:50,582
I'll bet this guy steals checks
out of mailboxes.

2881
02:14:50,582 --> 02:14:53,085
He washes off their names
and he puts on his own.

2882
02:14:55,087 --> 02:14:57,589
You're saying
that he's a local?

2883
02:14:57,589 --> 02:14:58,590
Well, if it were me,
you know

2884
02:14:58,590 --> 02:15:01,093
I'd call the bank first,
I'd check out the balance...

2885
02:15:01,093 --> 02:15:02,594
Make sure there's
enough money in there

2886
02:15:02,594 --> 02:15:04,096
